NOTICE OF MECHANIC'S LIEN
TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN:
RANDALL A.
I 195491:200UNGTON
UTAH COUNTY RECORDER
2001 Oct 17 8:37 am FEE 12.00 BY SS
RECORDED FOR ROBINSON SEILER & GLAZIER
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN that Jeff Hill Construction, Inc ., a Utah Corporation
(hereinafter referred to as the "Claimant"), of 41 West 530 South, Orem, Utah 84058, telephone
number (801)225-5321, hereby claims and intends to hold and claim a lien, pursuant to Chapter 1,
Title 38 of the Utah Code Annotated, as amended, upon all of the property located at 1789 North
1820 West, Provo, Utah County, State of Utah, which is more particularly described as follows:
Lot 41, Plat "F" GABLES AT GRANDVIEW SUBDIVISION, Provo, Utah,
according to the official plat thereof on file in the Utah County Recorder's Office,
Utah.
The purpose of Claimant's lien is to secure payment for the value of the services rendered, labor
performed, materials and equipment furnished or rented by the Claimant at the instance of the owner
and other persons and entities acting by the owner's authority as agent or contractor, until paid in
full, together with interest, costs, and attorney's fees as allowed by law.
1.
The name of the reputed owner of the property is Todd Daly and Cindy Daly.
2.
The name of the record owner of the property is Todd Daly and Cindy Daly.
3.
The name of the person by whom the Claimant was employed is Todd Daly and
Cindy Daly.
4.
The time when the first service was performed by the Claimant was April 12, 2001
5.
The time when the last service was performed by the Claimant was October 4, 2001.
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN, in accordance with $38-11-108 of the Utah Code, that under
Utah law an "owner" may be protected against liens being maintained against an "owner-occupied
residence" and from other civil action being maintained to recover monies owed for "qualified
services" performed or provided by suppliers and subcontractors as p
ors part of this contract if, and only
if, the following conditions are satisfied:
.. .
